 blend <b>30 sec\/speed 9<b>."},{"content":"Add stock paste, salt, pepper, cornflour and sugar, then cook <b>14 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>, placing simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid."},{"content":"Remove simmering basket, <strong>insert measuring cup<\/strong> and blend <b>15 sec\/speed 6<b>. Serve cabbage rolls immediately, topped with tomato sauce."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <em>The Basic Cookbook<\/em> or <em>Everyday Cookbook<\/em> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","1h 50m","10 pieces"]}